Package: libterm-size-any-perl
Version: 0.002-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Debian Perl Group <pkg-perl-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 22
Depends: perl, libdevel-hide-perl, libterm-size-perl-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/Term-Size-Any
Description: unified interface to retrieve the terminal size from Perl
 Term::Size::Any presents a unified interface to retrieve the terminal
 size in terms of characters or pixels. To do the job, it loads the first
 available module from a list of known alternatives, in this order:
     * Term::Size::Perl
     * Term::Size
     * Term::Size::ReadKey
